				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$0.002^{\circ}$\end{document}. These parameters have been included in an optical model of DKIST. We combined these polarizer imperfections (transmission, contrast, extinction angle) with spatial variations of the calibration retarders (transmission and elliptical retardance).

