				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$16\times40$\end{document}). However, we model a group of mirrors sharing incidence planes with tight alignment tolerances as just two variables. The retardance in the local Stokes-UV\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
