				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\pm0.1^{\circ}$\end{document}, which was easily achieved with our laser tracker, laboratory procedures, and on-Sun alignment procedures, as shown by Harrington et al. (2021a,b).

